[thinking] **Considering GraalVM native class loading**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about whether GraalVM native supports URLClassLoader. It seems like the native image does support classpath resource access but not class loading. I mean, `ClassLoader.loadClass` for classes known during the build could work. However, URLClassLoader might not load from jars at runtime in native images, possibly only from resources. It looks like loadClass would delegate to the parent first for test classes, which seems okay.
[thinking] 
